ZH: 我需要去药店买感冒药。
EN: I need to go to the pharmacy to buy cold medicine.

ZH: 这家药店很便宜。
EN: This pharmacy is very cheap.

ZH: 你知道这附近有没有24小时的药店吗？
EN: Do you know if there is a 24-hour pharmacy nearby?

ZH: 我们可以在药店里找到各种药物。
EN: We can find all kinds of medicine at the pharmacy.

ZH: 她去了药店买抗生素。
EN: She went to the pharmacy to buy antibiotics.

ZH: 这家药店的服务态度很好。
EN: The service attitude of this pharmacy is very good.

ZH: 他每天都要去药店购买药物。
EN: He goes to the pharmacy to buy medicine every day.

ZH: 这家药店提供免费送货服务。
EN: This pharmacy offers free delivery service.

ZH: 我们可以在药店买到处方药。
EN: We can buy prescription medicine at the pharmacy.

ZH: 药店里的药物都是经过严格检验的。
EN: The medicines in the pharmacy are all rigorously tested.

ZH: 在这家药店中，你可以找到各种口服药。
EN: In this pharmacy, you can find a variety of oral medications.

ZH: 去药店买药之前最好先询问医生。
EN: It is best to consult a doctor before going to the pharmacy to buy medicine.

ZH: 我们可以在药店里取得保健品。
EN: We can get health supplements at the pharmacy.

ZH: 这家药店有专门的老年人服务窗口。
EN: This pharmacy has a special service window for the elderly.

ZH: 药店里的药物价格实惠。
EN: The medicine prices at the pharmacy are reasonable.

ZH: 我们的家附近有一家新开的药店。
EN: There is a newly opened pharmacy near our house.

ZH: 在药店里购买药品最好带上处方。
EN: It is best to bring a prescription when buying medicine at the pharmacy.

ZH: 这家药店提供中英文双语服务。
EN: This pharmacy offers bilingual services in Chinese and English.

ZH: 药店工作人员总是很有耐心。
EN: The pharmacy staff are always very patient.

ZH: 去药店买药之前要检查药品的保质期。
EN: Check the expiration date of the medicine before going to the pharmacy to buy it.
